title: Comedy Nights With Kapil - Kapil ke Ghar, Sapno Ki Rani ( Queen)
description:
Plot
The roller coaster of laughs and fun starts with Kapil speaking on the various kinds of job and work he has adopted over a period of time, and has failed miserably. Kapil then asks the audience to share their experiences in various fields. Later, Kapil makes an announcement that he has decided to rob a bank and has asked his family members to share ideas on how to rob a bank. He calls out to his family members and Palak, Dadi and Raju appear on the scene, and spell out their ideas. Later, Kangana Ranaut, Rajkumar and the director, Vikas Bahl join Kapil onstage to promote their movie - Queen. Watch the show and enjoy.
